d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"Swimminghas\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"theWorld Anti-Doping Agency(Wada\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"its handling\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"positive test results\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"theTokyo Olympicsin\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story, reported by theNew York Timesand German news organization ARD, surrounds 23 Chinese swimmers, 11 of whom will compete at the ParisOlympics, testing positive for the heart medication trimetazidine (TMZ) during a training camp seven months out from the Tokyo Olympics in 2021.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.6543116845852497, \"rank\": 0.5267530299793177, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 890, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Das_Erste\", \"score\": 0.9999999998317435, \"rank\": 1.6820502826405764e-10, \"text\": \"ARD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Das_Erste\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Das_Erste\"}, {\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9978782890361554, \"rank\": 0.0021099362914198797, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The story\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"theNew York Timesand\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 864}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart medication trimetazidine\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"TMZ\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"a training camp\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the scandal has spilt over into the Paris Games, with Chinese swimmersupset at the \\\"tricks\\\" played by their rivals.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9978782890361554, \"rank\": 0.0021099362914198797, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scandal\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"tricks\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"their rivals\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has left many Chinese Zhang Yufei, a gold medalist in the women's 200-meter butterfly and 200-meter freestyle relay, and Wang Shun, who won gold in the men's 200-meter individual medley, are among those ready to compete in Paris, reportsNBC.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9978782890361554, \"rank\": 0.0021099362914198797, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9727864122998912, \"rank\": 0.027972027972023663, \"text\": \"Zhang Yufei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.